# News Summarization and Analysis Tool

## Overview
This tool retrieves news articles, summarizes them, and provides sentiment analysis and trending topics based on user queries.

## Features
- Fetch news articles from various sources.
- Generate concise summaries of news articles.
- Analyze the sentiment of articles.

